{"about_the_game":"Triumph in the Skies is a flight simulation game exclusive to VR. It makes flight learning easy and safe. Even rookies can drive training aircraft or fighters in many scenarios. Players can also use the keyboard to join the game in 2D mode. In addition, the game also has a lot of Chinese elements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real scenes:</h2>High-resolution landscape model, real exterior and interior plane model.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diversify game mode:</h2>Player can choose planes or scenes in Quick Start mode, follow the instruction and complete missions in Flying Career mode, challenge other pilot\u2019s record in Racing Mode\u2026\u2026tens of levels are waiting for you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various aircraft options:</h2>Stunt plane-comet<br>Cessna C-172<br>Su 33<br>More aircraft are constantly updated!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various scenes and tracks are optional:</h2>The landscape perfectly simulates a real city map.<br>The aircraft carrier landed in &quot;Liaoning&quot;, which was China's first aircraft carrier.<br>Hong Kong, China, Beijing Capital International Airport, Beijing Daxing International Airport.<br>More famous cities and airports are continuously updated!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Flight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1012580/f5e5186bcaf0ebbc71b39a669c252fd93cd9ecd7.jpg"},{"name":"Exploring Limits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1012580/2c76da5eecc0cc9113c3e6d8b90e2491ade98642.jpg"},{"name":"Ground","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1012580/0d461adf7b89bbc2d728325479c9a64554b88842.jpg"},{"name":"Dance On The Blade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1012580/d2a9ce6fa5a7903ef8a6a8e92a09b5bbd99ad580.jpg"},{"name":"Knows A Thing Or Two","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1012580/50141c414c8646f0200a3806543